These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, bike, quad-bike, skateboard
1. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
3. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Transport   | car | bike | quad-bike | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
City: hannover, nizza, marseilles, hamburg
1. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| City   | nizza | hannover | hamburg | marseilles |

 #################################

 
