.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, soul, rock, disco
1. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
2. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of disco##1
3. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Music-Genre   | soul | house | disco | rock |

