2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2  |   3    |     4     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | iced-tea | fanta | lemonade |

